   <body>
      <table colsep="1" rowsep="1">
         <desc>
            <p>The following table provides the workflow actions and status (current and subsequent status) of the <uicontrol>Program</uicontrol> record.</p>
            <p>For information on setting a workflow status to the next status, refer to <xref href="../../Common_Application_Features/Workflow_Management/WFStgTrans.xml">Workflow Status Transitions</xref>.</p>
         </desc>
         <tgroup cols="6">
            <colspec colname="c1" colnum="1"/>
            <colspec colname="c2" colnum="2"/>
            <colspec colname="c3" colnum="3"/>
            <colspec colname="c4" colnum="4"/>
            <colspec colname="c5" colnum="5"/>
            <colspec colname="c6" colnum="6"/>
            <thead>
               <row>
                  <entry>Phase</entry>
                  <entry>Current Workflow Status</entry>
                  <entry>Stakeholders</entry>
                  <entry>Action</entry>
                  <entry>Subsequent Workflow Status</entry>
                  <entry>Comments</entry>
               </row>
            </thead>
            <tbody>
               <row>
                  <entry>1</entry>
                  <entry>Draft</entry>
                  <entry>
                     <ul>
                        <li>Fund Manager</li>
                        <li>Program Manager</li>
                     </ul>
                  </entry>
                  <entry>Submit</entry>
                  <entry>Submitted</entry>
                  <entry>-</entry>
               </row>
               <row>
                  <entry morerows="1">2</entry>
                  <entry morerows="1">Submitted</entry>
                  <entry morerows="1">Fund Manager</entry>
                  <entry>Approve</entry>
                  <entry>Approved</entry>
                  <entry>On approval of a program, the following changes occur:<ul>
                        <li>The published budget estimates of the projects that are part of the program are approved. Also, thecurrent budget of each project is updated with the approved budget estimate items. </li>
                        <li>If what-if analysisis done, then the project start and end dates, forecast dates, and current budget datesare updated based on the forecast changes done in the program.  </li>
                        <li> The workflow status of each project that is part of the program is set to<uicontrol>Planned</uicontrol>if the start date of the project is not in the current yearand is set to <uicontrol>Pre-Award</uicontrol>if the start date of the project is in the current year. </li>
                        <li>A project is moved from the <uicontrol>Planned Projects </uicontrol>list to the <uicontrol>Projects </uicontrol>module list page if the workflow status of the project is set to <uicontrol>Pre-Award</uicontrol>. The project remains in the <uicontrol>Planned Projects </uicontrol>list page if the workflow status of the project is set to <uicontrol>Planned</uicontrol>. </li>
                        <li>Forecast snapshot is   generated automatically when the program is approved.</li>
                     </ul>
                  </entry>
               </row>
               <row>
                  <entry>Redraft</entry>
                  <entry>Draft</entry>
                  <entry>-</entry>
               </row>
               <row>
                  <entry morerows="1">3</entry>
                  <entry morerows="1">Approved</entry>
                  <entry morerows="1">Fund Manager</entry>
                  <entry>Close</entry>
                  <entry>Closed</entry>
                  <entry>-</entry>
               </row>
               <row>
                  <entry>Archive</entry>
                  <entry>Archived</entry>
                  <entry>Archived Programs are not available in the Program list page.</entry>
               </row>
            </tbody>
         </tgroup>
      </table>
